Overview  Service   Command 

Service: zimbraAdmin
Namespace: "urn:zimbraAdmin"
RenameUCService SOAP Command

Rename Unified Communication Service

Authorization token required true
Admin Authorization token required true

RenameUCServiceRequest

    <RenameUCServiceRequest> ## RenameUCServiceRequest
        <id>{id} (String)</id>
        <newName>{newName} (String)</newName>
    </RenameUCServiceRequest>

The following table describes elements and attributes you can define within a <RenameUCServiceRequest> element:

XPath Required / Optional Description
/id Required (only 1) Type:{id} (String)
Zimbra ID
/newName Required (only 1) Type:{newName} (String)
new UC Service name

RenameUCServiceResponse

    <RenameUCServiceResponse> ## RenameUCServiceResponse
        <ucservice name="{name}" id="{id}"> ## UCServiceInfo
            (<a n="{key}" /> ## Attr)*
         </ucservice>
    </RenameUCServiceResponse>

The following table describes elements and attributes you can define within a <RenameUCServiceResponse> element:

XPath Required / Optional Description
/ucservice Optional (0 or 1) Information about ucservice
/ucservice@name Required (only 1) Type:String
Name
/ucservice@id Required (only 1) Type:String
ID
/ucservice/a Optional (0 or more) Attributes
/ucservice/a@n Required (only 1) Type:String
Key
